msg: On the fsx-1.10 branch:  In FSX' DAG caching logic, introduce the notion
of a "normalized" path which is very easy to construct from any dirent.
This patch only uses normalized paths for cache lookup only while later
commits will extend that usage to open_path() and friends.
svn_fs_x__set_dag_node): Update callers to provide the normalized paths.
(try_match_last_node): Update caller to provide the normalized paths.
